<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Session Confirmed – Graphora</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #0f0f0f; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%); padding: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 26px; }
    .header p { margin: 8px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 15px; }
    .content { padding: 36px 32px; color: #e0e0e0; }
    .content h2 { color: #fff; margin-top: 0; }
    .detail-card { background: #242424; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #2e2e2e; font-size: 14px; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .detail-label { color: #888; }
    .detail-value { color: #e0e0e0; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn { display: block; width: fit-content; margin: 24px auto; padding: 14px 36px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; }
    .tip { background: #1e2a1e; border: 1px solid #2d4a2d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; color: #86efac; font-size: 13px; }
    .footer { background: #111; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #555; border-top: 1px solid #222; }
    .footer a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>✅ Session Confirmed!</h1>
      <p>Your mentorship session is booked and ready to go</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi {{studentName}},</h2>
      <p>Great news! Your session with <strong>{{mentorName}}</strong> has been confirmed. Here are the details:</p>

      <div class="detail-card">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Mentor</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{mentorName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Date & Time</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{scheduledAt}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Duration</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{duration}} minutes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Topic</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{topic}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Booking ID</span>
          <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip">
        💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> Join the session 2–3 minutes early to test your audio and video. The meeting link will be activated by your mentor when the session starts.
      </div>

      <a href="{{bookingUrl}}" class="btn">View Booking Details</a>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">Need to reschedule? You can cancel up to 24 hours before the session for a full refund.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
      <p>© 2025 Graphora. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
